snippet.title: Connie Nielsen cast as Hippolyta!! Amber Heard as Mera??
snippet.description:
Happy MLK Day, everybody, and welcome to another DC filled edition of the EdWord where today I'll be talking about my reaction to the casting of Connie Nielsen as Hippolyta and the tumors regarding Amber Heard as Mera. Thanks for watching and don't forget to subscribe. Hera, give them strength to subscribe!! Ha ha, also I realized I was saying the name of the Queen of Themyscara wrong and for that I apologize. Mistake corrected.

Batman v Superman: Dawn of Justice opens March 25th, and Wonder Woman opens June 23, 2017 and The Justice League Part One opens Nov 17, 2017
